Package org.monte.media.gui

Provides graphical user interface components.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ImagePanel Displays images on a panel.
JLabelHyperlinkHandler JLabelHyperlinkHandler makes HTML hyperlinks in a JLabel clickable.
JMovieControlAqua The MovieControlAqua contains an audio on/off button, a start/stop button, a slider, a forward and a rewind button, and a color cycling on/off button.
JMovieControlPanel JMovieControlPanel.
JMovieSliderAqua MovieSliderAqua.
JTimelineEditor JTimelineEditor visualizes the movie timeline, an insertion point and the start and end position of a movie clip.
Worker<T> This is an abstract class that you can subclass to perform GUI-related work in a dedicated event dispatcher.
